RELEASE OF MECHANIC'S AND MATERIALMAN'S LIEN
THE STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF TRAVIS
WHEREAS, on the 17th day of January, 2018, Beacon Sales Acquisition, Inc. dba Roofing
Supply Group ("lien claimant") caused-to be filed an Affidavit for Mechanic's and Materialman's
Lien in the Official Public Records of Travis County, Texas, said materialman's lien affidavit being
recorded as document 2018007100 of the Official Public Records of Travis County, Texas; said
materialman's lien affidavit covering the following described property located in Travis County,
Texas, to-wit:
Lot 4, McCann Annex No. 2;
and said materialman's lien affidavit reflecting the owner or reputed owner to be Pete S. & Anna M.
Morin; and
NOW, THEREFORE, said lien claimant, for good and valuable consideration, does hereby
release the above described materialman's lien.
